Title: Teen Beach Movie
Writer: Vince Marcello (story by), Mark Landry (story by), Vince Marcello (teleplay by), Mark Landry (teleplay by), Robert Horn (teleplay by)
Actors: Ross Lynch, Maia Mitchell, Gracie Gillam, Garrett Clayton
Plot: Two surfing lovers, whose doomed relationship is nearing to a close, find themselves swept into a a dimension traversing wave that sends them into a beach movie musical in the 60's.
